00125   bool check(std::string &msg) {
00126     bool success = true;
00127 
00128     map<MultiDataType, bool> validDataSets;
00129     validDataSets[CopyNumberMultiDataType] = true;
00130     validDataSets[GenotypeMultiDataType] = true;
00131     validDataSets[ExpressionMultiDataType] = true;
00132     validDataSets[CopyNumberVariationMultiDataType] = true;
00133     validDataSets[DmetCopyNumberMultiDataType] = true;
00134     validDataSets[DmetMultiAllelicMultiDataType] = true;
00135     validDataSets[DmetBiAllelicMultiDataType] = true;
00136 
00137     if(m_Generated.size() != m_Gold.size()) {
00138       return checkMsg(false, "CalvinChpCheck::check() - generated and gold vectors must be same size.",msg);
00139     }
00140     for(unsigned int i = 0; i < m_Generated.size(); i++) {
00141         try {
00142             m_Generated[i] = Util::convertPathName(m_Generated[i].c_str());
00143             m_Gold[i] = Util::convertPathName(m_Gold[i].c_str());
00144             CHPData chp1, chp2;
00145             CHPFileReader reader;
00146             reader.SetFilename(m_Generated[i]);
00147             reader.Read(chp1);
00148             reader.SetFilename(m_Gold[i]);
00149             reader.Read(chp2);
00150 
00151 
00152             string chp1Type = chp1.GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->GetFileTypeId();
00153             string chp2Type = chp2.GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->GetFileTypeId();
00154 
00155             success &= checkMsg(chp2Type == chp1Type, 
00156                                 "Error: Different CHP Types: " + chp2Type + ", " + chp1Type, msg);
00157 
00158             if (m_CheckHeaders && !headersSame(chp2, chp1, msg))
00159                     success = false;
00160 
00161             if(chp1Type == CHP_MULTI_DATA_TYPE) {
00162                 CHPMultiDataData generatedChp, goldChp;
00163                 CHPMultiDataFileReader chpReader;
00164                 chpReader.SetFilename(m_Generated[i]);
00165                 chpReader.Read(generatedChp);
00166                 chpReader.SetFilename(m_Gold[i]);
00167                 chpReader.Read(goldChp);
00168                     std::map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo> dataSets;
00169                     std::map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo>::iterator dataIter;
00170                 dataSets = generatedChp.GetDataSetInfo();
00171 
00172                 for(dataIter=dataSets.begin(); dataIter != dataSets.end(); dataIter++) {
00173                     if(validDataSets.find(dataIter->first) == validDataSets.end() || !(validDataSets.find(dataIter->first)->second)){
00174                         success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Unable to check multi data type '" + 
00175                                     StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataIter->first]) + "'", msg);
00176                     }
00177                 }
00178 
00179                 if(!multiDataCopyNumberSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, CopyNumberMultiDataType)) {
00180                     success = false;
00181                 }
00182                 if(!multiDataGenotypeSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, GenotypeMultiDataType)) {
00183                     success = false;
00184                 }
00185                 if(!multiDataExpressionSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, ExpressionMultiDataType)) {
00186                     success = false;
00187                 }
00188                 if(!multiDataCopyNumberVariationSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, CopyNumberVariationMultiDataType)) {
00189                     success = false;
00190                 }
00191                 if(!multiDataDmetCopyNumberSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, DmetCopyNumberMultiDataType)) {
00192                     success = false;
00193                 }
00194                 if(!multiDataDmetMultiAllelicSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, DmetMultiAllelicMultiDataType)) {
00195                     success = false;
00196                 }
00197                 if(!multiDataDmetBiAllelicSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg, DmetBiAllelicMultiDataType)) {
00198                     success = false;
00199                 }
00200             } else if(chp1Type == "affymetrix-quantification-analysis") {
00201                 CHPQuantificationData generatedChp, goldChp;
00202                 CHPQuantificationFileReader chpReader;
00203                 chpReader.SetFilename(m_Generated[i]);
00204                 chpReader.Read(generatedChp);
00205                 chpReader.SetFilename(m_Gold[i]);
00206                 chpReader.Read(goldChp);
00207                 if(!quantificationDataSame(goldChp, generatedChp, msg)) {
00208                     success = false;
00209                 }
00210             } else if(chp1Type == CHP_GENOTYPING_ASSAY_TYPE) {
00211                 success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Unable to compare CHPs of type " + chp1Type, msg);
00212             } else if(chp1Type == CHP_UNIVERSAL_ASSAY_TYPE) {
00213                 success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Unable to compare CHPs of type " + chp1Type, msg);
00214             } else if(chp1Type == CHP_RESEQUENCING_ASSAY_TYPE) {
00215                 success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Unable to compare CHPs of type " + chp1Type, msg);
00216             } else {
00217                 success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Unable to compare CHPs of type " + chp1Type, msg);
00218             }
00219         } // end try
00220         catch(Except &e) {
00221             success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: " + ToStr(e.what()),msg);
00222         }
00223         catch(affymetrix_calvin_exceptions::CalvinException &ce) {
00224             success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: AGCC library exception: " + 
00225                             StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(ce.Description()),msg);
00226         }
00227         catch(const std::exception &e) {
00228             success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: standard exception: " + ToStr(e.what()),msg);
00229         }
00230         catch(...) {
00231             success &= checkMsg(false, "Error: Uncaught Exception.",msg);
00232         }
00233     } // end for
00234     return success;
00235   }

00302   bool paramNamValTypeSame(ParameterNameValueType &gold, ParameterNameValueType &generated) {
00303     string goldName, genName, goldValue, genValue;
00304     /* For ease in debugger... */
00305     goldName = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(gold.GetName());
00306     genName = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(generated.GetName());
00307     goldValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(gold.ToString());
00308     genValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(generated.ToString());
00309     //    bool match = gold.GetName() == generated.GetName();
00310     bool match = true;
00311     if(gold.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType) {
00312         float goldFloat = gold.GetValueFloat();
00313         float genFloat = generated.GetValueFloat();
00314         double maxDiff = 0;
00315         checkFloat(goldFloat, genFloat, m_EpsParam, match, maxDiff);
00316     }
00317     // othewise compare as string.
00318     else {
00319         // ignore path separators.
00320         AffxByteArray baGold(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(gold.ToString()));
00321         AffxByteArray baGenerated(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(generated.ToString()));
00322         baGold.replace("\\", "/");
00323         baGenerated.replace("\\", "/");
00324         match &= baGold.toString() == baGenerated.toString();
00325     }
00326     return match;
00327   }

00335   bool paramVectorsSame(vector<ParameterNameValueType> &gold, vector<ParameterNameValueType> &generated) {
00336     bool match = true;
00337     if(gold.size() != generated.size())
00338       return false;
00339     for(int i = 0; i < gold.size(); i++) {
00340       match &= paramNamValTypeSame(gold[i], generated[i]);
00341     }
00342     return match;
00343   }

00346   bool ParameterNameValueTypeMostlySame(ParameterNameValueTypeVector &gold, ParameterNameValueTypeVector &test, 
00347                                         std::string &msg, std::wstring &prefix) {
00348     bool same = true;
00349     map<wstring,ParameterNameValueType> testMap;
00350     map<wstring,ParameterNameValueType>::iterator testMapIter;
00351     ParameterNameValueTypeVector::iterator goldIter; 
00352     ParameterNameValueTypeVector::iterator testIter;
00353     // Load up test as a map which will be queried by items in gold.
00354     for(testIter = test.begin(); testIter != test.end(); ++testIter) {
00355       testMap[testIter->GetName()] = *testIter;
00356     }
00357     for(goldIter = gold.begin(); goldIter != gold.end(); ++goldIter) {
00358       // ignore items that are in the ignoreMap
00359       if(m_IgnoreMap.find(goldIter->GetName()) == m_IgnoreMap.end()) {
00360         testMapIter = testMap.find(goldIter->GetName());
00361         if(testMapIter == testMap.end()) {
00362           msg += " Error: Test missing field: '" + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(goldIter->GetName()) + "'";
00363           same = false;
00364         }
00365         else {
00366           string goldName, genName, goldValue, genValue;
00367           /* For ease in debugger... */
00368           goldName = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(goldIter->GetName());
00369           genName = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(testMapIter->second.GetName());
00370           goldValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(goldIter->ToString());
00371           genValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(testMapIter->second.ToString());
00372           if(!paramNamValTypeSame(testMapIter->second, *goldIter) &&
00373             Util::fileRoot(genValue) != Util::fileRoot(goldValue)) {
00374             msg += " Error: for field '" + goldName + "' expecting: '" + goldValue + "' got: '" + genValue + "'";
00375             same = false;
00376           }
00377         }
00378       }
00379     }
00380     return same;
00381   }

00391   bool headersSame(CHPData &goldChp, CHPData &generatedChp, std::string &msgs) {
00392     bool success = true;
00393     FileHeader *goldHeader = NULL, *genHeader = NULL;
00394     goldHeader = goldChp.GetFileHeader();
00395     genHeader = generatedChp.GetFileHeader();
00396     /* Check the version. */
00397     success &= checkMsg(goldHeader->GetVersion() == genHeader->GetVersion(), "Error: different chp versions.", msgs);
00398 
00399     /* Check the group numbers. */
00400     success &= checkMsg(goldHeader->GetNumDataGroups() == genHeader->GetNumDataGroups(), 
00401                         "Error: Different group counts.", msgs);
00402 
00403     /* What type of array chp is from. */
00404     success &= checkMsg(goldChp.GetArrayType() == generatedChp.GetArrayType(), 
00405                         "Error: Different array types. [" + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(goldChp.GetArrayType()) + " != " + 
00406                         StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(generatedChp.GetArrayType()) + "]", msgs);
00407     
00408     /* Algorithm used. */
00409     success &= checkMsg(goldChp.GetAlgName() == generatedChp.GetAlgName(), 
00410                         "Error: Different algorithm names.", msgs);
00411     
00412     /* Algorithm version. */
00413     success &= checkMsg(goldChp.GetAlgVersion() == generatedChp.GetAlgVersion(), 
00414                         "Error: Different algorithm names.", msgs);
00415     
00416     
00417     ParameterNameValueTypeVector goldList = goldChp.GetChipSums();
00418     ParameterNameValueTypeVector genList = generatedChp.GetChipSums();
00419     success &= ParameterNameValueTypeMostlySame(goldList, genList, msgs, m_Prefix);
00420 
00421     goldList = goldChp.GetAlgParams();
00422     genList = generatedChp.GetAlgParams();
00423     success &= ParameterNameValueTypeMostlySame(goldList, genList, msgs, m_Prefix);
00424     return success;
00425   }

00427   void checkMultiDataDmetCopyNumberEntry(DmetCopyNumberData &goldEntry, DmetCopyNumberData &generatedEntry, 
00428                          bool &localSuccess, double &maxConfDiff, double &maxSignalDiff, int &numDiff) {
00429     if(goldEntry.name != generatedEntry.name) {
00430       localSuccess = false;
00431       reportError("Different names. gold: '" + goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name);
00432     }
00433 
00434     if(goldEntry.call != generatedEntry.call) {
00435       localSuccess = false;
00436       reportError("Different calls for cnv: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00437                   ToStr(goldEntry.call) + "' test: '" + ToStr(generatedEntry.call) + "'");
00438     }
00439 
00440     if(goldEntry.force != generatedEntry.force) {
00441       localSuccess = false;
00442       reportError("Different forced calls for cnv: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00443                   ToStr(goldEntry.force) + "' test: '" + ToStr(generatedEntry.force) + "'");
00444     }
00445 
00446     if(goldEntry.lower != generatedEntry.lower) {
00447       localSuccess = false;
00448       reportError("Different lower for cnv: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00449                   ToStr(goldEntry.lower) + "' test: '" + ToStr(generatedEntry.lower) + "'");
00450     }
00451 
00452     if(goldEntry.upper != generatedEntry.upper) {
00453       localSuccess = false;
00454       reportError("Different upper for cnv: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00455                   ToStr(goldEntry.upper) + "' test: '" + ToStr(generatedEntry.upper) + "'");
00456     }
00457 
00458     checkFloat(goldEntry.confidence, generatedEntry.confidence, m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxConfDiff);
00459     checkFloat(goldEntry.estimate, generatedEntry.estimate, m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxSignalDiff);
00460 
00461     if(!paramVectorsSame(goldEntry.metrics, generatedEntry.metrics)) {
00462       localSuccess = false;
00463       reportError("Param vectors different for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'.");
00464     }
00465 
00466     if(!localSuccess) {
00467       numDiff++;
00468     }
00469   }

00575 
00576     if(goldEntry.contextB != generatedEntry.contextB) {
00577       localSuccess = false;
00578       reportError("Different contextB for cnv: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00579                   ToStr(goldEntry.contextB) + "' test: '" + ToStr(generatedEntry.contextB) + "'");
00580     }
00581 
00582     checkFloat(goldEntry.confidence, generatedEntry.confidence, m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxConfDiff);
00583 
00584     checkFloat(goldEntry.signalA, generatedEntry.signalA, m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxSignalDiff);
00585     checkFloat(goldEntry.signalB, generatedEntry.signalB, m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxSignalDiff);
00586 
00587     if(!paramVectorsSame(goldEntry.metrics, generatedEntry.metrics)) {
00588       localSuccess = false;
00589       reportError("Param vectors different for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'.");
00590     }
00591 
00592     if(!localSuccess) {
00593       numDiff++;
00594     }
00595   }

00660   void checkMultiDataCopyNumberEntry(ProbeSetMultiDataCopyNumberData &goldEntry, ProbeSetMultiDataCopyNumberData &generatedEntry, 
00661                          bool &localSuccess, double &maxLog2RatioDiff, double &maxSmoothSignalDiff, double &maxAllelicDifferenceDiff, int &numDiff) {
00662     if(goldEntry.name != generatedEntry.name) {
00663       localSuccess = false;
00664       reportError("Different names. gold: '" + goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name);
00665     }
00666     if(goldEntry.chr != generatedEntry.chr) {
00667       localSuccess = false;
00668       reportError("Different Chromosome for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00669                   goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name + "'");
00670     }
00671     if(goldEntry.position != generatedEntry.position) {
00672       localSuccess = false;
00673       reportError("Different Position for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00674                   goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name + "'");
00675     }
00676     if (goldEntry.metrics.at(0).GetValueFloat() != generatedEntry.metrics.at(0).GetValueFloat()) {
00677       localSuccess = false;
00678       reportError("Different CNState for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00679                   goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name + "'");
00680     }
00681     if (localSuccess)
00682         checkFloat(goldEntry.metrics.at(1).GetValueFloat(), 
00683                    generatedEntry.metrics.at(1).GetValueFloat(), 
00684                    m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxLog2RatioDiff);
00685     if (localSuccess) 
00686         checkFloat(goldEntry.metrics.at(2).GetValueFloat(), 
00687                    generatedEntry.metrics.at(2).GetValueFloat(), 
00688                    m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxSmoothSignalDiff);
00689     if (localSuccess) 
00690         checkFloat(goldEntry.metrics.at(4).GetValueFloat(), 
00691                    generatedEntry.metrics.at(4).GetValueFloat(), 
00692                    m_EpsConfidence, localSuccess, maxAllelicDifferenceDiff);
00693     if ((goldEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat() == 0) || (goldEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat() == 1) ||
00694         (generatedEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat() == 0) || (generatedEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat() == 1)) {
00695         if (goldEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat() != generatedEntry.metrics.at(3).GetValueFloat()) {
00696           localSuccess = false;
00697           reportError("Different LOH for snp: '" + goldEntry.name + "'. gold: '" + 
00698           goldEntry.name + "' test: '" + generatedEntry.name + "'");
00699         }
00700     }
00701 
00702     if (!localSuccess) 
00703         numDiff++;
00704   }

00763   bool multiDataDmetCopyNumberSame(CHPMultiDataData &goldChp, CHPMultiDataData &generatedChp, std::string &msgs, MultiDataType dataType) {
00764     bool success = true;
00765     double maxDiff = -1;
00766     double maxSignalDiff = -1;
00767     int numDiff = 0;
00768     int goldNum = goldChp.GetEntryCount(dataType);
00769     int genNum = generatedChp.GetEntryCount(dataType);
00770     assert(dataType == DmetCopyNumberMultiDataType);
00771     Verbose::out(4, ToStr(goldNum) + " " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + " probesets.");
00772     if(!checkMsg(goldNum == genNum, "Wrong number of genotyping probesets.", msgs))
00773       return false;
00774     // if nothing to check, skip it.
00775     if(goldNum == 0)
00776       return true;
00777     for(int i = 0; i < goldNum; i++) {
00778       bool localSuccess = true;
00779       DmetCopyNumberData goldEntry, generatedEntry;
00780       goldChp.GetEntry(dataType, i, goldEntry);
00781       generatedChp.GetEntry(dataType, i, generatedEntry);
00782       checkMultiDataDmetCopyNumberEntry(goldEntry, generatedEntry, localSuccess, maxDiff, maxSignalDiff, numDiff);
00783       success &= localSuccess;
00784     }
00785     if(maxDiff > m_EpsConfidence)
00786       Verbose::out(1, "Max diff: " + ToStr(maxDiff) + " is greater than expected (" + ToStr(m_EpsConfidence) + ") [confidence]");
00787     if(maxSignalDiff > m_EpsConfidence)
00788       Verbose::out(1, "Max diff: " + ToStr(maxSignalDiff) + " is greater than expected (" + ToStr(m_EpsConfidence) + ") [signal]");
00789     if(numDiff > 0)
00790       Verbose::out(1, ToStr(numDiff) + " of " + ToStr(goldNum) + " (" + 
00791                    ToStr(100.0 * numDiff/goldNum) + "%) were different.");
00792     if(!success && m_DiffAllowed >= numDiff) 
00793         success = true;
00794     if(!success) {
00795       msgs += "Error: " + generatedChp.GetFilename() + " is different from " + goldChp.GetFilename() + ". ";
00796     }
00797     std::string res = "different";
00798     if(success) 
00799         res = "equivalent";
00800     Verbose::out(1, generatedChp.GetFilename() + ": " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + ": checked " + ToStr(goldNum) + " genotype entries.");
00801     Verbose::out(1, generatedChp.GetFilename() + ": " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + ": max confidence diff is: " + ToStr(maxDiff));
00802     Verbose::out(1, generatedChp.GetFilename() + ": " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + ": max signal diff is: " + ToStr(maxSignalDiff));
00803     Verbose::out(1, generatedChp.GetFilename() + ": " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + ": chip is " + res + ".");
00804     return success;
00805   }

01094     Verbose::out(1, generatedChp.GetFilename() + ": " + StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]) + ": chip is " + res + ".");
